During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Roark Garnet/Legends|Roark Garnet]] pretended to have contracted a phony ailment, '''Merthian lung infection''', on [[Lockest IV]] in an attempt to forestall a [[Imperial Office of Customs/Legends|customs]] inspection by [[Tax Inspector]] [[Mothra]]. The ruse worked, and the Tax Inspector beat a hasty retreat. Its supposed symptoms included a wheezing cough and a runny nose.<ref name="CP" />

